episodes.title: Epstein Survivors DISAPPOINTED: Victims Say the ‘Worst’ Parts Are ALL BLACKED OUT
episodes.description:
Thousands of long-awaited Jeffrey Epstein documents have finally been released, but survivors say the truth is still being hidden. With heavy redactions, missing files, and unanswered questions, victims are now accusing the Justice Department of failing transparency. Survivors and attorneys react to what’s been revealed, and what’s still blacked out, as outrage grows over whether justice is once again being delayed.
